 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{
  "Print", "[", "\"\<\n  PART A: pullback identity (3) verified.\n          \
BL form (SM 7) \[RightArrow] quasi-isotropic form (6) \n          coincides \
component by component.\n\n  PART B: NS-NS vacuum equations (1) verified in \
closed form\n          in BL coordinates:\n          - Eq1 (graviton):       \
10/10 components zero\n          - Eq2 (B-field):        6/6  components zero\
\n          - Eq3 (dilaton trace):  1/1  zero\n          - First integral (SM \
14): zero\n\n  CONCLUSION:\n    Since (1) are covariant (0,2)-tensor \
equations and\n    (3) defines a diffeomorphism on the exterior r > mbarj/2,\n\
    PART A + PART B together establish that the metric (6),\n    obtained as \
the pullback of (SM 7), satisfies (1) in\n    quasi-isotropic coordinates as \
well.\n\n    No independent verification of the QI form is required.\n\>\"", 
   "]"}], ";"}]}], "Input",
