Cell[BoxData["\<\"\\n  PART A: pullback identity (3) verified.\\n          BL \
form (SM 7) \[RightArrow] quasi-isotropic form (6) \\n          coincides \
component by component.\\n\\n  PART B: NS-NS vacuum equations (1) verified in \
closed form\\n          in BL coordinates:\\n          - Eq1 (graviton):      \
 10/10 components zero\\n          - Eq2 (B-field):        6/6  components \
zero\\n          - Eq3 (dilaton trace):  1/1  zero\\n          - First \
integral (SM 14): zero\\n\\n  CONCLUSION:\\n    Since (1) are covariant \
(0,2)-tensor equations and\\n    (3) defines a diffeomorphism on the exterior \
r > mbarj/2,\\n    PART A + PART B together establish that the metric (6),\\n \
   obtained as the pullback of (SM 7), satisfies (1) in\\n    quasi-isotropic \
coordinates as well.\\n\\n    No independent verification of the QI form is \
required.\\n\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9882269041477966`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"852d1442-f8e8-b047-b5ac-74d6a5af95b4"]
